{
  "_tutorial_zh": [
    "=== 武器事件脚本配置 ===",
    "此文件定义武器的特殊效果，使用 JavaScript 语法",
    "",
    "事件类型 (event)：",
    "  onHit: 攻击命中时触发",
    "  onKill: 击杀敌人时触发",
    "  onHurt: 自己被攻击时触发",
    "  whenHeld: 主手持有时触发 (每5tick)",
    "",
    "可用变量：",
    "  self: 持有武器的玩家/实体",
    "  victim: 受害者 (onHit/onKill) 或攻击者 (onHurt)",
    "  event: Forge事件对象",
    "",
    "_comment使用@前缀可从lang文件翻译"
  ],
  "_tutorial_en": [
    "=== Weapon Event Script Config ===",
    "This file defines special weapon effects using JavaScript syntax",
    "",
    "Event types (event):",
    "  onHit: Triggered when attack hits",
    "  onKill: Triggered when killing an enemy",
    "  onHurt: Triggered when you are attacked",
    "  whenHeld: Triggered while held in main hand (every 5 ticks)",
    "",
    "Available variables:",
    "  self: The player/entity holding the weapon",
    "  victim: The victim (onHit/onKill) or attacker (onHurt)",
    "  event: Forge event object",
    "",
    "_comment with @ prefix translates from lang file"
  ],

  "scripts": [
    {
    "_comment": "火焰锭双截棍效果 / Fiery Ingot Nunchaku Effects",
    "id": "fieryingotnunchaku",
      "events": [
        {
        "_comment": "@bstweaker.event.fire_on_hit",
          "event": "onHit",
        "actions": [
            "victim.setFire(3)"
        ]
        },
        {
        "_comment": "@bstweaker.event.strength_on_kill",
          "event": "onKill",
        "actions": [
            "self.addPotionEffect('minecraft:strength', 100, 0)"
        ]
        },
        {
        "_comment": "@bstweaker.event.damage_immunity",
        "event": "onHurt",
        "actions": [
            "event.setAmount(0)"
        ]
        },
        {
            "_comment": "@bstweaker.event.suppress_poison",
            "event": "whenHeld",
            "actions": [
                "var effects = self.getBadPotionEffects();",
                "for (var i = 0; i < effects.size(); i++) {",
                "  var eff = effects.get(i);",
                "  if (eff.getAmplifier() > 2) {",
                "    var id = eff.getPotionId();",
                "    var dur = eff.getDuration();",
                "    self.removePotionEffect(id);",
                "    self.addPotionEffect(id, dur, 2);",
                "  }",
                "}"
            ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
